How to access student emailIn order to access your Carl Albert State College email you will first need to reset your password.  At the upper right of the Vikeconnect portal, select "Reset Password".  Enter your information exactly as the examples given.  Once you have successfully reset your password you can select the "Student Email" link on the left hand navigation pane of Vikeconnect where you will be taken to the student email login page.  Enter the username and password provided when you reset your password and you will be logged into your CASC email account.
 
